                <span class="comment-copy">You've already been informed of the issue but you should probably read <a href="http://goo.gl/i8h6" rel="nofollow noreferrer">this</a> just to be totally informed.  The basic issue has to do with the theoretical "power" of the "machine" model of regular expressions versus what's required to parse a language like HTML. It has to do with language/automata theory.</span>
                
